    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某个失眠的夜晚，一位梦灵拜访了你，愿意帮助你回忆起你那美丽的一生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘与探索：</strong><br>通过拼凑玛雅的记忆，揭开她的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>流畅与放松：</strong><br>一款重新想象的拼图游戏，带来如流水般顺畅、治愈的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造玛雅的房间：</strong><br>在游戏中解锁纪念品，逐步改造玛雅的房间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>由获得英国电影和电视艺术学院提名的导演创作</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>拼凑玛雅的记忆</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款重新定义拼图游戏的作品，你将通过玛雅遗失的记忆拼出她的人生故事。<br>沉浸于层次丰富、流畅而治愈的玩法中，随着游戏推进，一切将悄然变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206730/extras/6c12e5daef225693d354a4fcaa4182c6.poster.avif?t=1746111560\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206730/extras/6c12e5daef225693d354a4fcaa4182c6.webm?t=1746111560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206730/extras/6c12e5daef225693d354a4fcaa4182c6.mp4?t=1746111560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用纪念品改变她的房间</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集记忆碎片，用它们改造玛雅的房间，打造一个温馨舒适的空间，映照她那丰富而美丽的一生。<br>帮助玛雅明白，她的人生从未空虚，而是充满意义与色彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206730/extras/b9ae6d49be8325b136f5661616b6ab29.poster.avif?t=1746111560\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206730/extras/b9ae6d49be8325b136f5661616b6ab29.webm?t=1746111560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206730/extras/b9ae6d49be8325b136f5661616b6ab29.mp4?t=1746111560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>揭开充满神秘与悬念的故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拼凑她生命中的17个章节，发现她动人的人生故事。<br>揭开她一生中的一个秘密，那是充满神秘与悬念的线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206730/extras/279841ffc9398ad75fcdc59cb569969d.avif?t=1746111560\" width=614 height=220 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一块拼图都是玛雅的一个记忆，通过它们，你将逐步拼出她的故事。<br>这是一个关于归属、爱、失去与意义的故事。<br>一款探索精神衰退影响的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206730/extras/ecc5e8d717657a6048118e22d32df9eb.avif?t=1746111560\" width=614 height=220 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开发者的话</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《浮现》（Emerge）是我在照顾祖母经历神经退行性疾病时创作的游戏。这是一段极其个人的经历，游戏试图探讨记忆的本质，以及失去它意味着什么。<br>我是一名来自苏格兰爱丁堡的独立开发者。希望你能喜欢《浮现》。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要我把这段整理成宣传海报形式或者本地化建议吗？</p>",
